<div class="banner-home"></div>
<div class="content-container mt-5 mx-auto">
  <div class="landing-page-container">
    <h1 class="action-title mb-4 px-5">Looking for a new creative space ?</h1>
    <%= render "shared/search" %>
    <div class="container w-100 py-5 ms-0 d-flex flex-column px-5">
      <div class="d-flex flex-md-row flex-column py-3">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-start pe-5">
          <h5 class="value-arting">Pop Up Your Creativity</h5>
          <p class="value-description">Our platform empowers artists to pop up their creativity by connecting them with other artists worldwide to swap ateliers. With our service, artists of all types can discover new places and gain inspiration for their art, opening up new horizons and creative environments to explore.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="img-values-container" >
          <%= image_tag("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611244420030-b22f359eee31?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=687&q=80", alt: "Someone starting to paint.")%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="d-flex flex-md-row flex-column py-3">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-start pe-5">
          <h5 class="value-arting">Make It Bloom</h5>
          <p class="value-description">Our platform encourages creativity by helping artists swap ateliers to learn new techniques, gain fresh perspectives, and develop their skills. Join us to make your talent bloom and take your art to the next level.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="img-values-container" >
          <%= image_tag("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1490186969638-fe0c8aea80bd?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1086&q=80", alt: "Painting brushes and flowers.")%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="d-flex flex-md-row flex-column py-3">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-start pe-5">
          <h5 class="value-arting">Swap It</h5>
          <p class="value-description">Our platform simplifies swapping by connecting you with like-minded artists who are interested in sharing ateliers. With a new space comes a new community, and our intuitive service makes it easy to find and connect with others. Swap with confidence and focus on your art, thanks to our secure and reliable platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="img-values-container">
          <%= image_tag("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580982333389-cca46f167381?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80", alt: "Two people sharing a creative space")%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="py-3 final-value">Join our platform today and start popping up your creativity, making it bloom, and swapping your atelier with other artists from around the world. Let's connect and create something beautiful together!</p>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="container px-5 py-3 ms-0 d-flex flex-column">
      <h5 class="text-dark fw-light pb-4 w-75 text-start">Testimonials</h5>
      <div class="d-flex flex-md-row flex-column">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column">
          <%= image_tag("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1489424731084-a5d8b219a5bb?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=687&q=80", class: "avatar-testimonial align-self-center", alt: "Profile picture of Leyla") %>
          <h5 class="text-dark fw-light pt-5 text-start">Leyla</h5>
          <p class="text-dark fw-light pt-5 text-start pe-2 testim-text">"Swapping studios through this platform was an amazing experience. I discovered a new creative environment, gained perspective, and made a new inspiring friend. The process was smooth and highly recommended for any artist looking to broaden their horizons."</p>
          <h5 class="text-dark fw-light pt-5 text-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-regular fa-star text-success"></i></i></h5>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column">
          <%= image_tag("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552374196-c4e7ffc6e126?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=687&q=80", class: "avatar-testimonial align-self-center", alt: "Profile picture of Stephan") %>
          <h5 class="text-dark fw-light pt-5 text-start">Stephan</h5>
          <p class="text-dark fw-light pt-5 text-start pe-2 testim-text">"Swapping my studio through this platform allowed me to discover new spaces and techniques, gain inspiration from other artists, and has been a game changer for me. Highly recommended for any artist seeking inspiration."</p>
          <h5 class="text-dark fw-light pt-5 text-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i></h5>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column">
          <%= image_tag("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523512090443-2d7df8b40358?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=687&q=80", class: "avatar-testimonial align-self-center", alt: "Profile picture of Tilla") %>
          <h5 class="text-dark fw-light pt-5 text-start">Tilla</h5>
          <p class="text-dark fw-light pt-5 text-start pe-2 testim-text">"Swapping my studio through this platform was easy and refreshing, connecting me with another artist in my area and helping me break out of a creative rut. Highly recommended for any artist looking to step out of their comfort zone."</p>
          <h5 class="text-dark fw-light pt-5 text-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star text-success"></i></h5>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
